sub_title: Junior Associate @ APROPOS - Advancing Process in Politics
summary: Thanks to my experience in local, national and international projects I have gained the strong foundation experience in project management, creative problem-solving, event management and policy advisory. I enjoy working with complex challenges, that is why I chose to study Management of International Social Challenges at Erasmus University Rotterdam and combine it with a masters in Innovation Sciences at Utrecht University. I am interested in gaining new, broadening and enriching experiences in the areas of policy, systemic change, social entrepreneurship, and process design.
